#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.53"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.53:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:0.2"
msgid "6. Nīvaraṇavagga "
msgstr "6. Hindrances "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.53:0.3"
msgid "53. Padhāniyaṅgasutta "
msgstr "53. Factors That Support Meditation "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.53:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, padhāniyaṅgāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five factors that support meditation. "

msgctxt "an5.53:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ: "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant has faith in the Realized One’s awakening: "

msgctxt "an5.53:1.4"
msgid "‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti. "
msgstr "‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:1.5"
msgid "Appābādho hoti appātaṅko; "
msgstr "They are rarely ill or unwell. "

msgctxt "an5.53:1.6"
msgid "samavepākiniyā gahaṇiyā samannāgato nātisītāya nāccuṇhāya majjhimāya padhānakkhamāya; "
msgstr "Their stomach digests well, being neither too hot nor too cold, but just right, and fit for meditation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:1.7"
msgid "asaṭho hoti amāyāvī; "
msgstr "They’re not devious or deceitful. "

msgctxt "an5.53:1.8"
msgid "yathābhūtaṃ attānaṃ āvikattā satthari vā viññūsu vā sabrahmacārīsu; "
msgstr "They reveal themselves honestly to the Teacher or sensible spiritual companions. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:1.9"
msgid "āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu; "
msgstr "They live with energy roused up for giving up unskillful qualities and embracing skillful qualities. They’re strong, staunchly vigorous, not slacking off when it comes to developing skillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:1.10"
msgid "paññavā hoti, udayatthagāminiyā paññāya samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā. "
msgstr "They’re wise. They have the wisdom of arising and passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending of suffering. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.53:1.11"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca padhāniyaṅgānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five factors that support meditation.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.53:1.12"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

